    {
      "kind": "content",
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Use these constants to control the conditions that allow fallback camera selection when you set the value of the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avcapturedevice/3875309-primaryconstituentdeviceswitchin"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " property to "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avcaptureprimaryconstituentdeviceswitchingbehavior/avcaptureprimaryconstituentdeviceswitchingbehaviorrestricted"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "When triggered by one or more enabled conditions, fallback camera switching waits for exposure and focus to stabilize before deciding which camera to use as the primary constituent device."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Whenever "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avcaptureprimaryconstituentdevicerestrictedswitchingbehaviorconditions/avcaptureprimaryconstituentdevicerestrictedswitchingbehaviorconditionvideozoomchanged"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " isn’t included in the restricted switching behavior conditions, "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avcaptureprimaryconstituentdeviceswitchingbehavior/avcaptureprimaryconstituentdeviceswitchingbehaviorrestricted"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " still allows camera selection when a change in video zoom factor makes a camera eligible or ineligible for selection as the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avcapturedevice/3875304-activeprimaryconstituentdevice"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ". "
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "When the video zoom factor decreases to below the switch-over zoom factor of the active primary constituent device, the system selects a different camera to satisfy the requested zoom factor. "
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "When the video zoom factor increases and crosses a camera’s switch-over zoom factor, this camera becomes eligible to set as the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avcapturedevice/3875304-activeprimaryconstituentdevice"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ". If exposure and focus allow, this camera then becomes the new active primary constituent device. Similar to the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/avfoundation/avcaptureprimaryconstituentdevicerestrictedswitchingbehaviorconditions/avcaptureprimaryconstituentdevicerestrictedswitchingbehaviorconditionvideozoomchanged"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " this also waits for exposure and focus to stabilize. Otherwise the activePrimaryConstituentDevice remains unchanged."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
